text:
Natsuha, are you okay now?
I received the photo data from the recent shoot...

Hehe, great expressions.
Both Kaho, Chiyoko, Juri, and Rinze...

When I wear this outfit...
I feel like I wanted to attend the same school as everyone.

Especially since there's quite an age gap with Kaho...
I do like our current relationship though.

...Attending the same school, huh?
Haha, sounds like it'd be a lively school.

Taking classes, having lunch together,
and going out to play after school...

Even then, I wonder if we would have crossed paths with
you somewhere, and formed a unit together with everyone...
